Here‚Äôs a **tracking lookup page** where users can input their tracking ID to view the status of their whistleblower report ‚Äî assuming reports are stored locally as encrypted `.enc` files (as in the previous setup).

---

## ‚úÖ Features

* Enter tracking ID
* Decrypt report
* Show metadata (not full message for security)
* Simple UI with Tailwind CSS

